T1  - The residual claim of rank and file employees
AU  - Rayton, Bruce A
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 9
IS  - 1
SP  - 129
EP  - 148
PY  - 2003
DA  - 2003/01/01/
SN  - 0929-1199
